o All documentation is in the /usr/doc/va-systemimager-* directory
o Read the HOWTO section of the manual:  
    "cd /usr/doc/va-systemimager-*"
    then "lynx ./manual/index.html" or similar.
o See the FAQ section of the manual if you still have questions
o To install on your imageserver run "./install"
o To install on your golden client run "./installclient"
